{
  "stem": "27770.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the Jews, I know were, plenty of them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In fact, my barrack was over 20 doctors.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jews, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All these under-commander who was feeding the crematorium, they were all mostly-- 80% doctors.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Doctors, dentists, a few lawyers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How it was possible-- I'll explain it to you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "End of '44, they-- first of all, there was a time when my sister-- between me and my sister was only one wire.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Later on, they took her to another camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we could go to-- and to talk to each other.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But later on, before the end, when they brought the last ghetto-- if I'm not mistaken, from Lodz, they brought a transport.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this transport came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the SS, who were-- who brought the people from this Lodz ghetto, they were Russian Mongolian-- Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they kept-- then they-- then they got to-- then the Germans took them in captivity.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They was willing to fight with the-- die with-- with the Germans against the Russian.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they made from them SS soldiers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when they saw already, the Germans, that the war is ending, the Russians are coming closer, those Mongolian Russian soldiers, who were dressed up in SS suits with guns, brought this transport from Lodz to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When they arrived, they took off their clothing, SS clothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They got the same stripes what's like the rest of the Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But in order they were helping the Germans, they gave them a special job.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they call it the [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[GERMAN] means they had-- it was a little wagon where all the food was distributed from one camp to another.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they were pushing these little wagons with stripes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They had enough food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They had clothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
